<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Public on LPP</title><link>https://blog.moro.kr/tags/public/</link><description>Recent content in Public on LPP</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.139.3</generator><language>ko-kr</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.moro.kr/tags/public/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>shortcat 를 발견하기 까지</title><link>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/shortcat-%EB%A5%BC-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B2%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EA%B9%8C%EC%A7%80/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/shortcat-%EB%A5%BC-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B2%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EA%B9%8C%EC%A7%80/</guid><description>&lt;p>레딧에서 우연히 [[vscode]] 익스텐션 이야기를 봤다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/vscode/comments/1ex57qy/i_moved_neovim_to_vscode_took_me_1_year_to_match/">https://www.reddit.com/r/vscode/comments/1ex57qy/i_moved_neovim_to_vscode_took_me_1_year_to_match/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://blog.moro.kr/assets/xfsnylt.png">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>이렇게 [[vimium]] 처럼 사용하면 좋을 것 같아서, 비슷한 익스텐션을 찾아보았다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>3년전 글에서 [[vimac]] 을 알게되었고, 이것이 [[homerow]]로 바뀌었다.&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>This is similar to vimium but for all mac apps &lt;a href="https://vimacapp.com/">https://vimacapp.com/&lt;/a>. I have seen it used to click around vscode&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://blog.moro.kr/assets/vym5j4a.png">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://blog.moro.kr/assets/hsloshi.png">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>[[Homerow]]를 사용하면 50번 마다 구매 팝업이 올라온다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>그래서 또 비슷한 앱을 찾게 되었고, [[Shortcat]] 을 발견하였다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://blog.moro.kr/assets/uzc1t3y.png">&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="homerow">homerow&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>homerow 에서 두가지 실행 방식이 있다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>logseq/Logseq Schrodinger 플러그인으로 배포하기</title><link>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/logseq/logseq-schrodinger-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</link><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/logseq/logseq-schrodinger-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="플러그인-설치">플러그인 설치&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/sawhney17/logseq-schrodinger">https://github.com/sawhney17/logseq-schrodinger&lt;/a> 설치&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/CharlesChiuGit/Logseq-Hugo-Template">https://github.com/CharlesChiuGit/Logseq-Hugo-Template&lt;/a> 템플릿 사용해서 저장소 생성&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="문서-작성">문서 작성&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>logseq에서 문서를 작성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>문서 속성에 &lt;code>public:: true&lt;/code> 를 추가한다&lt;/p>
&lt;p>필요에 따라 &lt;code>tags::&lt;/code>, &lt;code>categories::&lt;/code> 를 추가한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>예시)&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">public&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">tags&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">logseq&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">public&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">plugin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">ditto&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">sed&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">git&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">categories&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">logseq&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="다운로드">다운로드&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;code>export-public-pages-to-hugo&lt;/code> 버튼을 눌러서 다운로드 받는다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="배포">배포&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>다운받은 &lt;code>publicExport.zip&lt;/code> 압축을 풀면 아래 처럼 나온다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">├── assets
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│   └── golowgw.png#center
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">└── pages
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> ├── Logseq Schrodinger 플러그인으로 배포하기.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> ├── public.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> └── 카이젠 저니.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>저장소 경로를 설정하고 (&lt;code>$LOGSEQ_HUGO&lt;/code>)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>publicExport.zip 파일 압축 해제 후 커밋 &amp;amp; 푸시를 한다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>logseq schrodinger 플러그인으로 배포하기</title><link>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/logseq-schrodinger-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</link><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.moro.kr/pages/logseq-schrodinger-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>